relevant_findings.head: Normocephalic/atraumatic.
relevant_findings.eyes: No scleral icterus, mucous membranes moist.
relevant_findings.abdominal: Soft, nondistended, tender to palpation in RUQ, positive tenderness, nontender to percussion, no rebound tenderness, voluntary guarding in RUQ, distractible.
relevant_findings.extremities: No edema, warm and well perfused.
